{"tid":2065080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國連續21天無本地確診 解除全國宵禁","createTime":"2020-06-15T09:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:46:05.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7cde8f1596ee55dd51ca195463485a3c83ad4d","tid":2065080,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"泰國連續21天無本地確診 解除全國宵禁<br />\n2020-06-15 HKT 17:31<br />\n<br />\n泰國連續21日沒有錄得新型肺炎本地確診個案，今日起全國解除持續超過兩個月的宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n另外，少於120名學生的學校、主題公園、展覽館等今日起獲准重開，體育賽事亦可以恢復，但不設現場觀眾。餐廳可以恢復售賣酒精飲品，但酒吧與卡啦OK場所就要繼續關閉。<br />\n<br />\n泰國是中國以外，首個錄得新型肺炎病例的國家，自1月13日以來，累計超過3100人確診，58人死亡。報道指泰國政府正探討重啟旅遊業方案，包括透過雙邊協議建立「旅遊氣泡」，與疫情已受控的國家或地區恢復往來。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532183-20200615.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532183-20200615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7kXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=0c526a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532183-20200615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7ae5ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532183-20200615.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">看似安全，但檢測率非常低<br />\n<br />\nTest/1M pop:<br />\n6,708 (Thailand) vs 36,734 (Hong Kong)</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5ae016a5d9ede5e0b0cc033a263bcb785729669e","tid":2065080,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"快d開放中国人入境啦"},{"pid":"3a64a3908ac7157814df664141547d49d912e6bb","tid":2065080,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"香港：連續19天無本地確診後再有本地確診 消息指或會廷長限聚令14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}